## Feature Request

Support json configuration file for service limit overrides with multiple AWS accounts

### Feature Description

This feature request is a combination of #323 and #324. I'd be grateful if we could specify the service limit overrides for each account in a json configuration file something like that:

service_limits.json
```
{
    '<account_id>': {
        '<service_name>': {
          '<limit_name>': <value>,
          '<limit_name>': <value>
        },
        '<service_name>': {
          '<limit_name>': <value>,
          '<limit_name>': <value>
        },
        ...
    },
    '<account_id>': {
        '<service_name>': {
          '<limit_name>': <value>,
          '<limit_name>': <value>
        },
        '<service_name>': {
          '<limit_name>': <value>,
          '<limit_name>': <value>
        },
        ...
    },
    ...
}
